properties.flavorText: Held open by the Astral Crystal, you can safely return to the elemental plane.
The Astral Alliance knows the teleport to our world is exhausting. Please take a moment to rest here.

Looks good next to a magical house.
An elder SandwichArtist, guarding the ruins of the ancient sandwich shop.
A promotional poster for bread, tattered with age.
Left behind many years ago, when the astral portal was last closed.

Full of dark magic. But how does one harness the power of the turnip?
